nodes.text: Eric MacLennan is an actor know for his roles in Anna Karenina, Rogue One: A Star Wars Story, and Mary, Queen of Scots.
In 2016, MacLennan was hired to portray Tenzigo Weems (credited as Rebel Technician #1) in Rogue One: A Star Wars Story.
